songs.title: Talking To Myself
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Talking, talking, talking, talking, talking, talking
To myself

[Verse 1]
All alone
Nobody to just talk to
No skin, just bones
I'm seeing red, but I feel so blue

[Chorus]
Oh, i’m talking to myself
And got nobody else
All alone
And there ain't nothing on the shelf
I'm talking to myself, oh, i’m talking to myself
They all say "She's talking to herself"
To myself

[Verse 2]
I need a clone
I do, I don't
I'm already grown
Soemthing that's not known

[Chorus]
Oh, i'm talking to myself
And got nobody else
All alone
And there ain't nothing on the shelf
I'm talking to myself, oh, i’m talking to myself
They all say "She’s talking to herself"
To myself

[Bridge]
There ain't no way to go
Oh, I am on my own
Ain’t nobody wants to pick up the phone
I'm so blind ain't nothin shown

[Chorus/Outro]
Oh, i'm talking to myself
And got nobody else
All alone
And there ain’t nothing on the shelf
I'm talking to myself, oh, i'm talking to myself
They all say "She's talking to herself"
To myself
